Html:
I am making a winodws 8 phone application and trying to have a context menu on it from the Windows Phone tool kit.<br />
<br />
I been following this <a href="http://www.geekchamp.com/articles/listbox-contextmenu-with-mvvm-in-windows-phone" rel="nofollow">tutorial</a> but instead of list box I am using a long list selector that is built into WP8<br />
<pre><code>&lt;DataTemplate x:Key=&quot;GroceryListItemTemplate&quot;&gt;
    &lt;StackPanel Grid.Column=&quot;1&quot; Grid.Row=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;TextBlock x:Name=&quot;tbName&quot; TextWrapping=&quot;Wrap&quot; Text=&quot;{Binding Name}&quot; FontSize=&quot;32&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;TextBlock x:Name=&quot;tbProductInfo&quot; TextWrapping=&quot;Wrap&quot; Text=&quot;{Binding ProductInfoLabel}&quot; HorizontalAlignment=&quot;Left&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/StackPanel&gt;
    &lt;toolkit:ContextMenuService.ContextMenu&gt;
        &lt;toolkit:ContextMenu&gt;
            &lt;toolkit:MenuItem Header=&quot;Edit&quot; 
                    Command=&quot;{Binding GroceryItemsVm.EditGroceryItemCmd, Source={StaticResource Locator}}&quot;
                    CommandParameter=&quot;{Binding}&quot;/&gt;
            &lt;toolkit:MenuItem Header=&quot;Delete&quot; Command=&quot;{Binding GroceryItemsVm.DeleteGroceryItemCmd, Source={StaticResource Locator}}&quot;
                    CommandParameter=&quot;{Binding}&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;/toolkit:ContextMenu&gt;
    &lt;/toolkit:ContextMenuService.ContextMenu&gt;
&lt;/DataTemplate&gt;</code></pre>

above is a stripped down of what my code looks like<br />
<br />
here is my list selector<br />
<pre><code>&lt;phone:LongListSelector IsGroupingEnabled=&quot;True&quot; ItemsSource=&quot;{Binding GroceryItems}&quot;    HideEmptyGroups=&quot;True&quot; LayoutMode=&quot;List&quot; Grid.Row=&quot;1&quot;&gt;     
            &lt;phone:LongListSelector.ItemTemplate&gt;
                &lt;StaticResource ResourceKey=&quot;GroceryListItemTemplate&quot;/&gt;
            &lt;/phone:LongListSelector.ItemTemplate&gt;
&lt;/phone:LongListSelector&gt;
</code></pre>

Here is my mvvm code I have<br />
<pre><code>public class GroceryItemsVm : ViewModelBase
